Denser_Summary: This app discusses transportation services, specifically ride-hailing, with a focus on pricing, reliability, and customer service. Users have reported issues with prices being too high, drivers canceling rides, and poor customer service. Some users have had positive experiences with friendly drivers and timely pickups, but others have been left stranded or overcharged. The app's algorithm has been criticized for prioritizing profits over customer satisfaction, leading to frustration and disappointment among users.
